[English subtitles are available]

6
00:00:04,700 --> 00:00:05,000
[English subtitles are available]

7
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:07,940
My impressions...

8
00:00:09,300 --> 00:00:10,940
I think this job

9
00:00:10,980 --> 00:00:13,300
is different from how I imagined it before.

10
00:00:13,980 --> 00:00:16,260
They're not heroes who can do anything.

11
00:00:16,610 --> 00:00:18,180
They are also flesh and blood.

12
00:00:19,300 --> 00:00:21,420
They face more challenges than we do,

13
00:00:22,180 --> 00:00:24,620
but with their bravery
they still try to save everyone

14
00:00:25,060 --> 00:00:26,380
and never give up on anyone.

15
00:00:26,980 --> 00:00:28,660
What's left the biggest impression on you?

16
00:00:29,980 --> 00:00:31,580
What's left the biggest impression...

17
00:00:34,660 --> 00:00:35,980
Probably this group of lovely people

18
00:00:35,980 --> 00:00:36,980
that I've become friends with.

19
00:00:37,060 --> 00:00:38,580
I don't care what anyone else

20
00:00:38,580 --> 00:00:40,180
came here for.

21
00:00:40,580 --> 00:00:42,620
Some may want this to be a springboard.

22
00:00:43,090 --> 00:00:45,300
Some may want to start a fauxmance

23
00:00:45,300 --> 00:00:45,980
and gain publicity.

24
00:00:46,420 --> 00:00:47,900
But I came here

25
00:00:48,300 --> 00:00:49,500
and saw the hard work

26
00:00:49,540 --> 00:00:51,580
that firefighters do on a daily basis,

27
00:00:52,020 --> 00:00:53,980
and their courage to sacrifice themselves

28
00:00:54,380 --> 00:00:55,740
for others

29
00:00:55,820 --> 00:00:57,460
in emergency situations.

30
00:00:57,980 --> 00:01:01,260
I think they're extremely noble

31
00:01:02,100 --> 00:01:03,380
and selfless.

32
00:01:04,260 --> 00:01:05,100
Maybe...

33
00:01:05,740 --> 00:01:07,660
this is what I came here for.

34
00:01:13,620 --> 00:01:14,620
Here, Ms. Xu.

35
00:01:15,100 --> 00:01:15,980
Thank you.

36
00:02:25,780 --> 00:02:28,970
[Bright eyes in the Dark]

37
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:33,220
[Episode 14: What Do Instructors Instruct On?]

38
00:02:34,730 --> 00:02:37,460
[Toilet]

39
00:02:40,980 --> 00:02:41,500
What are you looking at?

40
00:02:41,540 --> 00:02:42,940
Be quick. You'll be scolded again.

41
00:02:46,380 --> 00:02:48,060
What is this place?

42
00:02:48,090 --> 00:02:49,260
What did I say?

43
00:02:49,260 --> 00:02:50,260
There must be something wrong.

44
00:02:51,660 --> 00:02:52,660
Well,

45
00:02:53,100 --> 00:02:55,380
Chen Yilong actually tried
to act in front of me.

46
00:02:56,100 --> 00:02:57,260
A bit naive, isn't he?

47
00:02:58,060 --> 00:02:59,260
You're so impressive, Ran.

48
00:02:59,260 --> 00:03:00,700
Nothing gets past you.

49
00:03:00,980 --> 00:03:01,540
Look.

50
00:03:01,820 --> 00:03:04,380
He was in denial because he was afraid
of being found out.

51
00:03:04,380 --> 00:03:06,820
There is trash everywhere.

52
00:03:08,340 --> 00:03:09,940
I mean...

53
00:03:10,570 --> 00:03:12,940
we should just expose it.

54
00:03:13,380 --> 00:03:14,100
But...

55
00:03:14,100 --> 00:03:15,700
don't you think the temperature in here

56
00:03:15,780 --> 00:03:17,200
is a bit too high?

57
00:03:17,420 --> 00:03:19,140
I feel like my makeup is running.

58
00:03:19,500 --> 00:03:20,380
Yeah.

59
00:03:20,380 --> 00:03:22,140
It's so stuffy.

60
00:03:22,380 --> 00:03:24,340
This place is even hotter
than the last one.

61
00:03:28,940 --> 00:03:29,860
Here, Zhiyi.

62
00:03:30,380 --> 00:03:31,140
Film me.

63
00:03:31,580 --> 00:03:32,100
Over there.

64
00:03:32,100 --> 00:03:32,660
What am I filming?

65
00:03:32,660 --> 00:03:33,260
Stand over there.

66
00:03:33,260 --> 00:03:34,580
Now, you're going to film me.

67
00:03:35,260 --> 00:03:37,940
Find an ideal angle and film me.

68
00:03:37,940 --> 00:03:39,940
We'll film a take for each one of us

69
00:03:39,980 --> 00:03:40,980
and send them to the crew.

70
00:03:40,980 --> 00:03:43,100
The ratings of this episode
depend on the three of us.

71
00:03:45,340 --> 00:03:47,500
Why would anyone carry that around?

72
00:03:47,940 --> 00:03:48,540
Dai.

73
00:03:49,260 --> 00:03:50,260
He has a point.

74
00:03:53,220 --> 00:03:54,100
Ready?

75
00:03:57,980 --> 00:03:58,540
Fire!

76
00:03:58,580 --> 00:03:59,420
There's a fire!

77
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:00,500
There's a fire!

78
00:04:00,500 --> 00:04:01,260
Hurry up!

79
00:04:01,260 --> 00:04:01,980
Ran!

80
00:04:02,060 --> 00:04:03,340
Let's go!

81
00:04:03,380 --> 00:04:05,340
Rolling. Action!

82
00:04:17,260 --> 00:04:18,340
Ran,

83
00:04:18,780 --> 00:04:21,100
that was so cool!

84
00:04:21,100 --> 00:04:22,780
It makes me feel so safe!

85
00:04:25,380 --> 00:04:26,580
Hello, everyone.

86
00:04:27,220 --> 00:04:29,660
I'm Fire Safety Inspector Ran Dongyang.

87
00:04:30,460 --> 00:04:33,340
Today, we're conducting
a fire safety inspection

88
00:04:33,340 --> 00:04:35,220
at Yilong Food Processing Factory.

89
00:04:35,660 --> 00:04:36,660
But just now,

90
00:04:36,660 --> 00:04:38,810
I came across a safety hazard.

91
00:04:38,810 --> 00:04:39,780
But don't worry,

92
00:04:39,780 --> 00:04:42,220
I've put out the fire.

93
00:04:42,220 --> 00:04:43,010
That's right.

94
00:04:44,260 --> 00:04:45,530
I would like to remind everyone

95
00:04:45,900 --> 00:04:48,820
that fire safety
is everyone's responsibility.

96
00:04:52,100 --> 00:04:52,700
Do I look good?

97
00:04:53,020 --> 00:04:53,580
Yes.

98
00:04:56,100 --> 00:04:56,780
Nan Chu.

99
00:04:58,260 --> 00:04:58,980
Go back now.

100
00:04:58,980 --> 00:04:59,700
Or you'll get scolded again.

101
00:05:00,340 --> 00:05:01,900
I just saw Ran Dongyang and the other two

102
00:05:01,900 --> 00:05:02,660
go that way.

103
00:05:05,140 --> 00:05:06,460
What are they up to this time?

104
00:05:06,900 --> 00:05:07,780
Shall we go take a look?

105
00:05:07,780 --> 00:05:08,140
Let's go.

106
00:05:09,340 --> 00:05:10,380
One more. We'll try somewhere else.

107
00:05:10,380 --> 00:05:11,220
One more?

108
00:05:11,220 --> 00:05:12,020
One more.

109
00:05:12,020 --> 00:05:12,780
Come here.

110
00:05:13,220 --> 00:05:13,700
Come on.

111
00:05:16,660 --> 00:05:17,580
One more.

112
00:05:21,380 --> 00:05:22,660
Come on, burn up.

113
00:05:23,540 --> 00:05:24,700
Why is there another...

114
00:05:24,700 --> 00:05:25,450
Ran Dongyang!

115
00:05:25,780 --> 00:05:26,540
Are you guys crazy?

116
00:05:26,540 --> 00:05:27,340
Setting a fire here?

117
00:05:27,700 --> 00:05:28,700
What are you doing?

118
00:05:29,140 --> 00:05:30,380
Nan Chu, what are you doing?

119
00:05:30,380 --> 00:05:31,260
What are you doing?

120
00:05:31,260 --> 00:05:32,700
Honestly, Yang,

121
00:05:32,700 --> 00:05:34,020
what an eventful life you're trying to live.

122
00:05:34,580 --> 00:05:35,580
What do you mean?

123
00:05:35,580 --> 00:05:36,660
Go back now.

124
00:05:37,210 --> 00:05:37,780
I'm not leaving.

125
00:05:37,780 --> 00:05:38,890
Leave if you want.

126
00:05:38,890 --> 00:05:40,100
Just ignore her, Ran.

127
00:05:41,580 --> 00:05:42,140
Let's go.

128
00:05:45,780 --> 00:05:46,700
Stop!

129
00:05:48,100 --> 00:05:48,980
Get out of my way.

130
00:05:48,980 --> 00:05:49,780
No.

131
00:05:50,660 --> 00:05:51,700
Are you going to tell on us?

132
00:05:51,700 --> 00:05:52,220
Go away.

133
00:05:52,220 --> 00:05:52,900
No.

134
00:05:52,970 --> 00:05:54,340
Nan Chu, watch your attitude!

135
00:05:54,340 --> 00:05:55,780
All right. Calm down, everyone.

136
00:05:57,140 --> 00:05:58,780
Mr. Jiang, you are a pro.

137
00:05:58,780 --> 00:06:01,020
Isn't dramatic effect
the most important thing to a show?

138
00:06:01,460 --> 00:06:02,700
If Lin Luxiao comes,

139
00:06:03,660 --> 00:06:04,140
I...

140
00:06:04,140 --> 00:06:05,460
I'll have done all this for nothing.

141
00:06:05,780 --> 00:06:06,220
Yeah.

142
00:06:06,220 --> 00:06:07,700
We're doing this
for the show's dramatic effect.

143
00:06:07,780 --> 00:06:08,140
Yeah.

144
00:06:08,220 --> 00:06:09,570
But that's not the way to do it.

145
00:06:09,570 --> 00:06:10,980
Have you got no safety awareness?

146
00:06:11,220 --> 00:06:12,220
Go away now!

147
00:06:12,820 --> 00:06:13,700
Wait.

148
00:06:14,460 --> 00:06:17,020
Why is there smoke under this door?

149
00:06:20,380 --> 00:06:22,340
Go!

150
00:06:33,900 --> 00:06:34,780
What is that place?

151
00:06:35,780 --> 00:06:37,140
It's a w-warehouse.

152
00:06:37,140 --> 00:06:37,900
Is there anyone inside?

153
00:06:37,980 --> 00:06:39,380
I think there's a renovation team.

154
00:06:39,380 --> 00:06:39,820
Zheng Yang.

155
00:06:39,900 --> 00:06:40,340
Yes.

156
00:06:40,340 --> 00:06:40,980
Contact Command Center.

157
00:06:40,980 --> 00:06:41,220
Yes.

158
00:06:41,540 --> 00:06:42,260
Where are the others?

159
00:06:42,700 --> 00:06:43,460
Find them now!

160
00:06:43,460 --> 00:06:44,340
Everyone, evacuate!

161
00:06:44,380 --> 00:06:44,900
Evacuate!

162
00:06:44,900 --> 00:06:45,140
OK.

163
00:06:45,140 --> 00:06:46,020
Evacuate!

164
00:06:46,020 --> 00:06:47,260
Stop filming! Go!

165
00:06:47,660 --> 00:06:48,900
Do you know what's going on?

166
00:06:48,980 --> 00:06:50,020
I don't know either.

167
00:06:50,020 --> 00:06:51,020
Get in the truck and get changed!

168
00:07:00,780 --> 00:07:01,660
Nan Chu.

169
00:07:01,980 --> 00:07:02,580
Are you all right, Nan Chu?

170
00:07:02,580 --> 00:07:03,820
I'm fine.

171
00:07:08,580 --> 00:07:09,580
Help!

172
00:07:10,260 --> 00:07:11,100
Help!

173
00:07:13,540 --> 00:07:14,140
The door won't open.

174
00:07:14,140 --> 00:07:15,460
What happened?

175
00:07:15,460 --> 00:07:16,580
Why is it locked?

176
00:07:16,660 --> 00:07:17,260
The door won't open!

177
00:07:17,260 --> 00:07:18,260
Come and help.

178
00:07:18,380 --> 00:07:18,780
Hurry!

179
00:07:18,780 --> 00:07:19,780
Open the door!

180
00:07:21,780 --> 00:07:22,700
Open the door!

181
00:07:23,700 --> 00:07:25,700
Come and help! Open the door!

182
00:07:28,220 --> 00:07:29,020
It's going to hurt a little.

183
00:07:31,100 --> 00:07:31,900
Open the door!

184
00:07:33,340 --> 00:07:34,780
Open the door! Is anyone there?

185
00:07:35,900 --> 00:07:36,700
Is anyone there?

186
00:07:47,340 --> 00:07:48,220
Hurry up!

187
00:07:50,700 --> 00:07:51,540
Get the fire hoses ready,

188
00:07:51,540 --> 00:07:52,340
and the rescue kit.

189
00:07:52,380 --> 00:07:52,900
Yes!

190
00:07:53,700 --> 00:07:54,540
Get the fire hoses. Let's go!

191
00:07:54,980 --> 00:07:55,660
Where are the other few of you guys?

192
00:07:55,660 --> 00:07:56,260
Requesting permission to rescue.

193
00:07:56,260 --> 00:07:58,020
There's a fire at Yilong
Food Processing Factory.

194
00:07:58,220 --> 00:07:59,460
The number of people trapped
is not yet known.

195
00:07:59,900 --> 00:08:01,540
Heping Road Special Division Station
has dispatched a truck.

196
00:08:01,540 --> 00:08:02,460
Firefighting is underway.

197
00:08:02,460 --> 00:08:03,140
Requesting backup.

198
00:08:08,050 --> 00:08:08,810
Hello?

199
00:08:09,780 --> 00:08:10,540
Director Lin,

200
00:08:10,980 --> 00:08:12,580
we're in the disused warehouse
behind the toilet.

201
00:08:12,780 --> 00:08:13,700
Behind the toilet?

202
00:08:13,780 --> 00:08:14,570
What's going on in there?

203
00:08:15,340 --> 00:08:16,540
There's a big fire here,

204
00:08:16,900 --> 00:08:17,900
and there are many combustible items.

205
00:08:18,020 --> 00:08:18,700
OK, got it.

206
00:08:18,700 --> 00:08:19,260
I'll be right there.

207
00:08:19,340 --> 00:08:20,220
Remove the door!

208
00:08:20,220 --> 00:08:20,700
Yes!

209
00:08:26,700 --> 00:08:27,340
Hurry up!

210
00:08:28,220 --> 00:08:28,940
Cool it down!

211
00:08:30,060 --> 00:08:30,820
Hurry up!

212
00:08:36,210 --> 00:08:37,340
Make it higher!

213
00:08:40,860 --> 00:08:43,340
The fire is getting bigger.

214
00:08:52,810 --> 00:08:53,980
Don't panic.

215
00:08:54,060 --> 00:08:55,220
We've learned how to save ourselves.

216
00:08:55,220 --> 00:08:57,340
Lower your body and wait for help.

217
00:09:06,460 --> 00:09:07,620
Hurry up!

218
00:09:09,100 --> 00:09:10,420
Help!

219
00:09:10,700 --> 00:09:11,980
Hurry up!

220
00:09:11,980 --> 00:09:13,820
Come on!

221
00:09:13,940 --> 00:09:14,940
Come on! Over there!

222
00:09:15,700 --> 00:09:16,620
Keep going!

223
00:09:17,220 --> 00:09:17,980
Help!

224
00:09:17,980 --> 00:09:18,580
Where is he?

225
00:09:19,620 --> 00:09:20,820
-Where are you?
-Over here!

226
00:09:22,180 --> 00:09:22,820
Over here!

227
00:09:22,820 --> 00:09:23,420
Over there!

228
00:09:24,300 --> 00:09:25,460
Hurry up!

229
00:09:27,980 --> 00:09:28,820
Are you all right?

230
00:09:28,820 --> 00:09:29,820
Come on.

231
00:09:35,300 --> 00:09:37,820
Why are the firefighters still not here yet?

232
00:09:38,060 --> 00:09:40,060
Are we going to die here?

233
00:09:41,420 --> 00:09:42,940
I'm so scared!

234
00:09:49,060 --> 00:09:50,060
I have an idea!

235
00:09:50,100 --> 00:09:51,420
Find something to knock the wall.

236
00:09:51,420 --> 00:09:52,580
This wall is soft.

237
00:09:52,580 --> 00:09:53,980
We can make holes on it and climb out.

238
00:09:55,340 --> 00:09:56,460
Find something.

239
00:09:56,820 --> 00:09:57,980
Over there!

240
00:09:58,060 --> 00:09:58,860
There's a stick here.

241
00:09:58,940 --> 00:10:00,100
There's another one on the ground.

242
00:10:01,010 --> 00:10:03,530
[Rescue]

243
00:10:13,860 --> 00:10:14,940
Reinforcements in place.

244
00:10:14,940 --> 00:10:15,820
About to enter the fire scene.

245
00:10:16,210 --> 00:10:17,100
Hurry up!

246
00:10:17,100 --> 00:10:18,580
Come on!

247
00:10:18,580 --> 00:10:19,740
Get the equipment ready!

248
00:10:19,740 --> 00:10:20,580
Hurry!

249
00:10:25,340 --> 00:10:25,820
Hurry up!

250
00:10:25,820 --> 00:10:27,420
Make it higher!

251
00:10:27,420 --> 00:10:28,300
Higher!

252
00:10:32,620 --> 00:10:33,340
Mr. Ran,

253
00:10:33,420 --> 00:10:34,060
get up here!

254
00:10:34,460 --> 00:10:35,860
What for?

255
00:10:36,500 --> 00:10:38,220
You'll shoulder me and get me up there.

256
00:10:38,820 --> 00:10:41,340
Why isn't it the other way around?

257
00:10:41,340 --> 00:10:43,340
You know how good he is at climbing.

258
00:10:43,820 --> 00:10:44,460
Yes.

259
00:10:44,460 --> 00:10:46,820
He's even better than Director Lin
at climbing.

260
00:10:46,820 --> 00:10:47,460
Hurry up.

261
00:10:47,460 --> 00:10:48,220
Come on. Hurry up.

262
00:10:48,220 --> 00:10:49,410
Give me a hand.

263
00:10:53,740 --> 00:10:54,980
Up there!

264
00:10:56,100 --> 00:10:56,820
Hurry up!

265
00:10:57,620 --> 00:10:58,420
Hurry up!

266
00:10:58,420 --> 00:10:58,980
Over there!

267
00:10:59,340 --> 00:11:01,170
Let's go!

268
00:11:01,620 --> 00:11:03,420
These two are wounded. Hurry up!

269
00:11:05,220 --> 00:11:05,940
Let's go!

270
00:11:05,940 --> 00:11:06,580
Come on!

271
00:11:06,580 --> 00:11:07,980
Hurry!

272
00:11:07,980 --> 00:11:08,940
You're safe now.

273
00:11:08,940 --> 00:11:10,180
Follow me!

274
00:11:11,100 --> 00:11:12,220
Keep going.

275
00:11:12,300 --> 00:11:13,460
Hurry!

276
00:11:13,460 --> 00:11:14,340
That way!

277
00:11:14,340 --> 00:11:15,130
Higher!

278
00:11:15,980 --> 00:11:17,700
One, two, three!

279
00:11:25,860 --> 00:11:26,700
Be careful!

280
00:11:29,340 --> 00:11:30,980
Hurry up! I can't hold on much longer!

281
00:11:31,100 --> 00:11:31,980
Almost there!

282
00:11:32,060 --> 00:11:32,940
A little higher.

283
00:11:33,300 --> 00:11:35,980
Hurry up! The fire is getting closer!

284
00:11:36,340 --> 00:11:37,100
Stand still!

285
00:11:37,100 --> 00:11:38,300
Hurry up!

286
00:11:40,180 --> 00:11:41,420
The fire is getting bigger.

287
00:11:42,820 --> 00:11:43,610
Be careful!

288
00:11:43,820 --> 00:11:45,420
Come on, Mr. Jiang!

289
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:50,410
He did it!

290
00:11:50,430 --> 00:11:51,300
Great!

291
00:11:53,460 --> 00:11:54,100
The rope!

292
00:11:59,100 --> 00:12:00,460
W-Why are you going up first?

293
00:12:00,500 --> 00:12:01,340
I'll climb up first

294
00:12:01,340 --> 00:12:02,700
and then pull you guys up.

295
00:12:02,700 --> 00:12:03,820
