00:42:13,810 --> 00:42:16,620
[Tips for Fire Safety]

886
00:42:16,650 --> 00:42:18,330
Factories are densely populated places

887
00:42:18,620 --> 00:42:20,100
with many flammable
and combustible items.

888
00:42:20,660 --> 00:42:22,650
How should we save ourselves

889
00:42:22,660 --> 00:42:25,260
in the unfortunate event of a fire?

890
00:42:25,860 --> 00:42:26,840
First of all,

891
00:42:26,850 --> 00:42:28,470
stay calm.

892
00:42:29,010 --> 00:42:31,290
All factories are equipped
with firefighting facilities.

893
00:42:31,680 --> 00:42:34,180
Make initial firefighting attempts
immediately

894
00:42:34,340 --> 00:42:36,860
and call 119 to report the fire.

895
00:42:37,420 --> 00:42:40,180
Stay calm during the evacuation process.

896
00:42:40,740 --> 00:42:41,900
Follow the instructions

897
00:42:42,340 --> 00:42:44,860
and evacuate in an orderly manner.

898
00:42:45,460 --> 00:42:46,060
In your daily life,

899
00:42:46,260 --> 00:42:49,180
familiarize yourself with the locations
of fire exits and evacuation routes,

900
00:42:49,740 --> 00:42:51,860
so that you can easily find them
in an emergency.

901
00:42:52,860 --> 00:42:53,900
When there is smoke,

902
00:42:54,260 --> 00:42:56,860
cover your mouth and nose with a wet towel

903
00:42:56,860 --> 00:42:58,340
and bend over as you walk towards the exit.

904
00:42:59,580 --> 00:43:01,100
If you have to wait for rescue,

905
00:43:02,060 --> 00:43:02,620
make sure

906
00:43:03,020 --> 00:43:06,860
that you stand on a terrace
or at a window

907
00:43:06,940 --> 00:43:08,980
and signal for help.
